        {
            "title": "標普500指數上演4月來最大逆轉 交易員試圖探尋背後原因",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"804\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gK2_Kb1L8qhyM1zF_nMe8g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0b7af26ec16cf6db4f72bf03fcf94f19\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 處於人工智能競爭核心地位的晶片製造商發布的業績令人驚艷。就業報告證實美國經濟依然穩健。全球最大零售商的季度財報表明消費者仍在支出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管種種跡象表明美股將迎來風險偏好升溫的一日，但交易大廳的樂觀情緒並未持續太久。標普500指數在開盤一小時後一度上漲1.9%，但隨後抹去漲幅，到下午1點下跌1.1%，創下自4月市場動盪以來最大反轉，市值蒸發超過2萬億美元。VIX指數升破28。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關於此次股市走勢反轉的原因眾說紛紜。一些交易員指出，人們再度擔憂人工智能能否帶來足夠的收入或利潤以支撐對該技術的巨額投入。一些人認為比特幣自4月以來首次跌破87,000美元是導致股市暴跌的部分原因。一些股票交易員則表示，他們擔心股票估值過高，以及臨近周五期權到期日，市場波動性可能會加劇。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f1a0f245-6b2d-3e50-bef2-71173ce0d712-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"804\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/odIbz.6KUmupcEhV3Mdj6Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0b7f9deed66d74e07576a1a6c653320a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是華爾街分析師、策略師和交易員對周四股市劇烈波動的看法：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">海納國際集團衍生品策略聯席主管Chris Murphy：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“随着英伟达财报尘埃落定，而美联储12月降息的可能性不大，投资者开始质疑还有什么因素能推动年底上涨。据说商品交易顾问(CTA)的持仓情况仍较脆弱；系统性策略整体仍小幅净做多，但若出现更深层回调，可能触发进一步的抛售。”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">PenderFund Capital Management首席投資官Greg Taylor：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“我认为早盘的乐观情绪其实主要是空头回补推动的。现在，市场开始冷静地重新思考。”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Miller Tabak + Co. LLC首席市場策略師Matt Maley：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“人工智能的盈利能力是否真达到像市场消化的水平？这是关键问题。交易员担心当下对人工智能的投资能否在五年后带来利润。因此，许多人开始表示，‘我得先一定程度上获利了结。’”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bokeh Capital Partners LLC首席投資官兼創始人Kimberly Forrest：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“这确实引人深思：既然如此火爆，那为什么你的利润却没能体现出来呢？”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Piper Sandler首席市場技術員Craig Johnson：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“英伟达财报公布后，投资者松了一口气。然而，广义市场仍需更多时间才能趋于稳定并开始回升。”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題TradersSearchForCluesBehindBiggestS&amp;PReversalSinceApril</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE500%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%944%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%8B%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-203126156.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 05:40:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "比特幣自4月以來首次跌破8.7萬美元 加密貨幣市場延續跌勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JK8eunG8RnSiQ_.yLA9vMQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/774b61f322a8681289a3f608f492a93c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 加密貨幣市場周四延續逾一個月的跌勢，正值美國股市也全部回吐當天早些時候錄得的漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣下跌逾4%，自4月以來首次跌破8.7萬美元。市場難以吸引新的買盤，而今年早些時候支撐價格的動能基本消退。這輪回調發生在短線交易者連續數周平倉，以及10月創紀錄上漲後遺留持倉尚未消化之際，使市場更易受到拋壓和劇烈波動影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「加密貨幣正遭遇遵循四年周期邏輯的巨鯨投資者的大舉拋售，而這一階段通常是價格下跌的時點，」CoinShares研究主管James Butterfill表示。「儘管我們並不認為這種理論在基本面上成立，但這已然成為某種自我實現的預言，大額持有者9月以來拋售超過200億美元的資產。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-04c7bcda-a326-36d1-aa92-40121a9e6e0e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S68PcVifPmm4Fx8UnBkkcA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/903345da367f4daa3d4215058a981421\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在輝達業績利好引發新一輪AI狂熱後，美股一度飆升，但隨即回吐漲幅。市場對AI估值過高的擔憂，以及對聯儲會能否在12月降息的疑慮，導致華爾街波動加劇。與此同時，加密市場仍陷於內部去槓桿和散戶需求衰退的困境。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一跌勢促使期權交易者關注8.5萬美元關口。據Coinbase旗下加密交易所Deribit的期權合約數據顯示，該價位的下行保護需求最大，其次為8.2萬美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Crypto Market Extends Slide With Bitcoin Dropping Below $87,000</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E8%87%AA4%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B48-7%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%8C%E5%8B%A2-195537844.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 05:25:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
